Award-winning singer Tiwa Savage has sold out the tickets for her forthcoming North American tour. The number one African bad girl announced via her Instagram page that tickets for her “Water and Garri” had sold out in Toronto, Canada. The concert is billed for June 19, 2022.   David Guetta hops on Goya Menor’s hit track     Teamwork not segregation is needed in music industry, says…     Niyi Akinmolayan’s Anthill partner Adia for Hey You   Tiwa also provided a link to purchase tickets for the remaining locations on the tour leg. “We already sold out Toronto #WaterAndGarriTour. Ticket link for other cities in my bio,” she wrote. In March, the “Somebody’s Son” singer unveiled details of her North America tour. The Afropop singer’s forthcoming tour, “Water and Garri” which also happens to be the name of her 2021 EP will officially kick off in New York on May 15 and wrap-up in Toronto on June 19, 2022.